title: Colder (01 - 05) (complete) (2012 - 2013) (- Nem -)
description:
A five-part mini-series written by Paul Tobin, illustrated by Juan Ferreyra, and originally published by Dark Horse Comics in 2012-2013. 
 
Colder is an original horror comic about insanity and the world crazy people live in and of course Declan Thomas who's body temperature is so low and cold he should not even be among the living anymore. He has not said anything for the past five years but one day he decides it is time to start talking again. That's when the story begins to heat-up!
